# Field encryption at rest (A47) — REQUIRED in production. Encrypts provider
# credentials (Shopify tokens, Stripe webhook secret + read key). Comma-
# separated Fernet keys; first encrypts, all decrypt (rotation). Generate with:
#   python -c "from cryptography.fernet import Fernet; print(Fernet.generate_key().decode())"
